data.description: This beautiful 2-story, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in the Caroleton subdivision is a must see! The first floor offers an open concept for the great room, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for entertaining with easy access to the covered patio and fenced backyard. The kitchen features granite countertops, an island, and stainless steal appliances. A large flex room/office space and powder room complete the first floor. The master suite, 3 other bedrooms with spacious closets, laundry room and full bath are upstairs. The master bathroom features double sinks, garden tub and tiled glass-front shower. This home is energy efficient with the Energy Star certification, has plenty of storage space, and windows throughout for natural lighting. The subdivision offers many amenities to include a pool, sidewalks, and easy access to Ft Gordon. Click to submit an application. Available for move in TODAY!
